                     <interp inst="t17960217-4-off15" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960217-4-cd16" type="crimeDate">29th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-4-off15 t17960217-4-cd16"></join>, two pair of women's leather shoes, value 7s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17960217-4-victim80" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Sluter
               <interp inst="t17960217-4-victim80" type="surname" value="Sluter"></interp>
